<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Pulse" MadCap:lastBlockDepth="6" MadCap:lastHeight="285" MadCap:lastWidth="946">
    <body>
        <ol>
            <li>Select the <span class="Emphasis">Skill Requests</span> tab. Any requests from users are listed on the tab.</li>
            <li>
                <p>To approve a request, do the following:</p>
                <ol class="LowerAlpha">
                    <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Approve</span>.</li>
                    <li>In the dialog that opens, you can associate the skill with a category (if you have created one).</li>
                    <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Approve Skill</span>.</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>To reject a request, do the following:</p>
                <ol class="LowerAlpha">
                    <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Reject</span>.</li>
                    <li>In the dialog that opens, you can type a reason for the rejection.</li>
                    <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Reject Skill</span>.</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>